    <h1>Support</h1>
    <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> March 18, 2026</p>

    <h2>1. Welcome to Promi Teleprompter Support</h2>
    <p>
        Thank you for using Promi Teleprompter!  
        We’re here to help you with any questions, issues, or feedback regarding the app.
    </p>

    <h2>2. How Promi Teleprompter Works</h2>
    <p>
        Promi Teleprompter allows you to write or paste your script and display it on screen while recording or presenting.
        All scripts and content are handled locally on your device.
    </p>

    <h2>3. Common Issues and Solutions</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Text Not Scrolling</strong>: Make sure scrolling speed is set correctly and playback is started.</li>
        <li><strong>App Performance Issues</strong>: Restart the app and ensure your device has enough available storage.</li>
        <li><strong>Recording Problems</strong>: Check that camera and microphone permissions are enabled in device settings.</li>
        <li><strong>Subscription Not Active</strong>: Tap "Restore Purchases" to sync your subscription.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Subscriptions and Purchases</h2>
    <p>
        Promi Teleprompter offers optional premium features via subscription.
        All payments are securely handled through Apple In-App Purchases.
    </p>
    <p>
        If your subscription is not recognized, please use the <strong>"Restore Purchases"</strong> option in the app.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Contact Support</h2>
    <p>
        If you need help, please contact us at:
        <br>
        <a href="mailto:tugberktabak@yahoo.com"><strong>tugberktabak@yahoo.com</strong></a>
    </p>
    <p>
        To help us resolve your issue faster, please include:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>Your User ID (if available)</li>
        <li>A short description of the issue</li>
        <li>Screenshots or screen recordings (if possible)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
        We aim to respond within 24–48 hours.
    </p>

    <h2>6. Feature Requests and Feedback</h2>
    <p>
        We’re constantly improving Promi Teleprompter.
        If you have suggestions or feature requests, feel free to reach out via email.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Troubleshooting Tips</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Make sure you are using the latest version of the app.</li>
        <li>Restart your device if you encounter unexpected issues.</li>
        <li>Ensure permissions (camera, microphone) are properly enabled.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>8. Escalation</h2>
    <p>
        If your issue is not resolved within 48 hours, please follow up with additional details.
        For urgent requests, you may include <strong>"Urgent"</strong> in your email subject.
    </p>
